{
  "texts": [
    "We further evaluate the model's performance on coding tasks using HumanEval (Chen et al., 2021) and MBPP (Austin et al., 2021).",
    "The results, presented in Table 1, show that InfoPO consistently outperforms both DPO and SimPO.",
    "This further indicates that InfoPO is more suitable for enhancing reasoning abilities compared to DPO and SimPO.",
    "We also assess the performance of InfoPO on summarization and dialogue generation tasks.",
    "As shown in Table 2, InfoPO demonstrates substantial improvements over the baseline models in both tasks."
  ]
}